First Time push : Follow the instructions given below the repo
To create a new branch and switch to it : git checkout -b "branchname"
To update the branch :

git add . ->to add all the changed files
git commit -m -> to  commit that change with a message
git checkout "branchname that you wanna switch to"-> to switch to a particular branch

git pull origin main -> To update all the changes that are made in main (Optional)

git merge "branchname"-> this branchname will be merged to the main

git push origin main -> to push the updated main to github

git push -u origin "branchname"-> to push this branch to github(not necessary to merge it to main)



